quran[227]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,“Tâ-Sîn-Mîm
  26,2,“Izi ndi Ayah (ndime) za buku (la Qur’an) lofotokoza chilichonse (chofunika m’chipembedzo)
  26,3,"“Mwina iwe (Mtumiki Muhammad {s.a.w}) udziononga wekha (ndi madandaulo) chifukwa chakuti (iwo) sadakhale okhulupirira"
  26,4,"“Tikadafuna, tikadawatsitsira chizizwa kuchokera kumwamba; kotero kuti makosi awo akadadzichepetsa ndi chizizwacho, (sakadatha kucheukira kwina koma sitifuna kukakamiza anthu kuti akhale Asilamu)"
  26,5,“Ndipo palibe pamene chikuwadzera chivumbulutso chatsopano chochokera kwa (Allah) Wachifundo chambiri koma amazipatula ku icho (chivumbulutso)
  26,6,“Ndithu atsutsa; choncho posachedwapa ziwadzera nkhani zomwe adali kuzichitira chipongwe
  26,7,"“Kodi sadaone nthaka? Ndimmera ungati taumeretsa m’menemo kuchokera mu mtundu ulionse, wokongola"
  26,8,“Ndithu m’zimenezo muli zizindikiro (zosonyeza mphamvu za Allah). Koma ambiri a iwo sali okhulupirira
  26,9,"“Ndipo, ndithu Mbuye wako ndi Mwini mphamvu zoposa; Wachisoni chosatha"
  26,10,"“Ndipo (akumbutse) pamene Mbuye wako adaitana (m’neneri) Mûsa; adamuuza: “Pita kwa anthu ochita zoipa.”"
  26,11,"“Anthu a Farawo; (auze): “Kodi sawopa (Allah)?”"
  26,12,"“(Mûsa) adati: “Mbuye wanga! Ine ndikuopa kuti anganditsutse"
  26,13,"“Ndipo chingabanike chifuwa changa (ndi maganizo, chifukwa chakunditsutsa kwawo); ndiponso lirime langa siliyankhula momveka bwino. Choncho tumizaninso uthengawu kwa Harun (kuti tikhale awiri ndipo azikandithangata pantchito yangayi)"
  26,14,“Ndipo iwowo ndili nawo mlandu ndipo ndikuopa kuti angandiphe (pobwezera chimene ndidawalakwira powaphera munthu wawo)
  26,15,"“(Allah) adati: “Iyayi! Pitani pamodzi ndi zozizwa Zathu; ndithu Ife tikakhala nanu limodzi (pokuthangatani) uku tikumvetsera (zimene azikanena).”"
  26,16,"““Choncho mpitireni Farawo, ndipo kamuuzeni kuti: “Ife ndi atumiki a Mbuye wa zolengedwa zonse.”"
  26,17,““(Tatumidwa) kuti uwapereke kwa ife ana a Israyeli (kuti tinke nawo ku Sham).”
  26,18,"“(Farawo) adati (kwa Mûsa): “Kodi sitidakulere kwathu uli mwana, ndi kukhala nafe pa moyo wako zaka zambiri?”"
  26,19,"““Ndipo udachita chochita chako chimene udachichita, ndipo iwe ndiwe mmodzi wa osathokoza!”"
  26,20,"“(Mûsa) adati: “Ndidachita zimenezo pomwe ine ndidali mmodzi wa osazindikira zinthu.”"
  26,21,"““Choncho ndidakuthawani pomwe ndidakuopani; tsono Mbuye wanga wandipatsa nzeru zoweruzira (zinthu), ndi kundisankha kukhala mmodzi wa atumiki.”"
  26,22,““Ndipo kodi umenewu ndimtendere wonditonzera pomwe mudawaika muukapolo ana a Israyeli!”
  26,23,"“Farawo adati: “Kodi ndani Mbuye wa zolengedwayo?”"
  26,24,"“(Mûsa) adati: “Mbuye wa thambo ndi nthaka ndi zapakati pake, ngati muli ndi chitsimikizo. (Amachita chilichonse m’menemo mmene wafunira; kupereka moyo ndi imfa).”"
  26,25,"“(Farawo) adauza omwe adali m’mphepete mwake (mwachipongwe): “Kodi simukumva (mawu achibwanawa)?”"
  26,26,"“(Mûsa adapitiriza kunena) adati: “Allah ndi Mbuye wanu komanso Mbuye wamakolo anu oyamba.”"
  26,27,"“(Farawo) adati (kwa anthu ake pofuna kuwakwiitsa): “Ndithu Mtumiki wanu amene watumidwa kwa inu, ngwamisala.”"
  26,28,"“(Mûsa) adati: “Mbuye wakuvuma ndi kuzambwe, ndi zomwe ziri pakati pake ngati mumazindikira (zinthu, muzindikira izi).”"
  26,29,"“(Farawo) adati: “Ngati udzipangira mulungu wina kusiya ine, ndikuchita kukhala mmodzi wa omangidwa kundende.”"
  26,30,"“(Mûsa) adati: “Kodi ngakhale nditakubweretsera chinthu choonekera poyera (chosonyeza kuti zimene ndikunenazi ndizoona ndatumidwa ndi Allah)?”"
  26,31,"“(Farawo) adati: “Chibweretse, ngati uli mwa onena zoona.”"
  26,32,"“Ndipo (Mûsa) adaponya (pansi) ndodo yake, mwadzidzidzi idasanduka njoka yopenyeka"
  26,33,“Ndipo adatulutsa dzanja lake; pompo lidali loyera (kwambiri) kwa (onse) openya
  26,34,"“(Farawo) adauza akuluakulu omwe adali m’mphepete mwake: “Ndithu uyu ndi wamatsenga wodziwa kwambiri.”"
  26,35,““Akufuna kukutulutsani m’dziko lanu ndi matsenga ake; kodi nanga mukuti chiyani?”
  26,36,"“(Anthu) adati (kwa Farawo): “Mpatse nthawi ndi m’bale wakeyo, ndipo tumiza (amithenga) m’mizinda yonse osonkhanitsa anthu.”"
  26,37,““Ndipo akubweretsera amatsenga onse odziwa kwabasi (kotero kuti adzampambana Mûsa).”
  26,38,“Choncho amatsenga adasonkhanitsidwa mu nthawi ya tsiku lodziwika
  26,39,"“Ndipo anthu adauzidwa: “Kodi inu musonkhana? (Choncho, sonkhanani).”"
  26,40,““Mwina tingawatsatire amatsenga ngati iwo ndiamene apambane.”
  26,41,"“Ndipo pamene amatsenga adadza, adati kwa Farawo: “Kodi tidzakhala ndi mphoto ngati ife ndife tipambane?”"
  26,42,"“(Farawo) adati: “Inde, (ndipo kuonjezera apo) ndithu inu mudzakhala mwa amene amakhala pafupi (ndi ine, monga nduna zanga).”"
  26,43,"“Mûsa adati kwa iwo: “Ponyani zimene mufuna kuponya (zosonyeza kuya kwa matsenga anu).”"
  26,44,"“Choncho adaponya zingwe zawo ndi ndodo zawo, ndipo adati: “Kupyolera mu mphamvu za Farawo, ndithu ife ndife opambana.”"
  26,45,“Kenako Mûsa adaponya ndodo yake; mwadzidzidzi iyo idameza zabodza zomwe iwo adakonza
  26,46,“Pamenepo amatsenga adadzigwetsa pansi molambira
  26,47,"“Adati: “Tamkhulupirira Mbuye wa zolengedwa.”"
  26,48,““Mbuye wa Mûsa ndi Harun.”
  26,49,"“(Farawo) adati: “Ha! Mwamkhulupirira chotani ndisanakulolezeni? Ndithu iyeyu ndimkulu wanu amene adakuphunzitsani matsenga. Choncho posachedwa mudziwa (chimene ndikuchiteni) ndithu ndidula manja anu ndi miyendo yanu mosinthanitsa (podula mkono wakumanja ndi mwendo wakumanzere; kapena kudula mkono wakumanzere ndi mwendo wakumanja), ndipo kenako ndikupachikani nonsenu.”"
  26,50,"“(Amatsenga) adati: “Palibe vuto, ndithu ife (tonse) tibwerera kwa Mbuye wathu.”"
  26,51,““Ndithu ife tikuyembekezera kuti Mbuye wathu atikhululukire zolakwa zathu; pokhala oyamba mwa okhulupirira.”
  26,52,"“Ndipo tidamvumbulutsira Mûsa (kuti): “Pita ndi anthu anga m’nthawi yausiku (musamuke m’dziko la Iguputo); ndithu inu mutsatidwa.”"
  26,53,“Choncho Farawo adatuma (owatuma) kuti asonkhanitse anthu m’mizinda (kuti aletse ana a Israyeli kutuluka)
  26,54,"“(Adawauza otumidwa aja kuti auze anthu kuti): “Ndithu awa (ana a Israyeli) ndikagulu kochepa"
  26,55,“Ndipo ndithu iwo akutikwiitsa
  26,56,“Koma ndithu ife tonse (ndife ochuluka komabe ngakhale zili choncho) tikuwaopa.”
  26,57,“Choncho tidawatulutsa m’minda ndi mwa akasupe
  26,58,“Ndi m’nkhokwe za chuma ndi m’malo okongola
  26,59,“Momwemo ndi mmene tidawachitira ndipo tidawalowetsera chokolo zinthu zawo zonse kwa ana a Israyeli
  26,60,“Choncho (anthu a Farawo ndi iye mwini) adawatsatira (ana a Israyeli) dzuwa litatuluka
  26,61,"“Ndipo pamene magulu awiri adaonana (anthu a Farawo ndi anthu a Mûsa), anthu a Mûsa adati: “Ndithu ife tigwidwa.”"
  26,62,"“(Mûsa) adati: “Iyayi! Ndithu Mbuye wanga ali nane pamodzi. Andiongolera (kuti ife tonse tipulumuke).”"
  26,63,"“Ndipo tidam’vumbulutsira mawu Mûsa (akuti): “Menya nyanja ndi ndodo yako.” Ndipo idagawikana, mbali iliyonse idali ngati phiri lalikulu"
  26,64,"“Ndipo tidawayandikitsa pamenepo anthu enawo, (Farawo ndi anthu ake nalowa pa njira yomweyo pambuyo pa Mûsa ndi anthu ake)"
  26,65,"“Ndipo tidapulumutsa Mûsa ndi onse amene adali nawo (mpaka adaoloka nyanjayo, madzi ali chiimire mbali iyi ndi iyi)"
  26,66,"“Kenako tidawamiza enawo, (Farawo ndi anthu ake)"
  26,67,“Ndithu pa zimenezi pali lingaliro. Koma ambiri a iwo sali okhulupirira
  26,68,"“Ndipo, ndithu Mbuye wako ndi Mwini mphamvu zoposa (amalanga ndi chilango choopsa omwe amunyoza); Wachisoni (kwa omkhulupirira ndi kumumvera)"
  26,69,“Ndipo awerengere (osakhulupirira) nkhani ya (M’neneri) Ibrahim
  26,70,“Pamene adafunsa bambo wake ndi anthu ake (kuti); “Kodi mukupembedza chiyani?”
  26,71,"“Adati: “Tikupembedza mafano; ndipo tipitiriza kuwapembedza.”"
  26,72,"“(Ibrahim) adati: “Kodi amakumvani mukawaitana?”"
  26,73,““Kapena amakuthandizani (mukawapembedza) kapena amapereka masautso kwa inu (mukasiya kuwapembedza)?”
  26,74,"“(Iwo) adati: “Koma tidapeza makolo athu akuchita zimenezi.”"
  26,75,"“(Ibrahim) adati: “Kodi mukuwaona awa amene mwakhala mukuwapembedza,”"
  26,76,““Inu ndi makolo anu amene adatsogola?”
  26,77,"““Ndithu iwo ndiadani anga, kupatula Mbuye wa zolengedwa zonse;”"
  26,78,"““Yemwe adandilenga, ndiponso Yemwe akundiongolera (kunjira yolungama);”"
  26,79,““Ndiyemwe akundidyetsa ndi kundimwetsa.”
  26,80,““Ndipo ndikadwala ndiyemwe amandichiritsa.”
  26,81,"““Ndi Amene adzandipatsa imfa, ndipo (tsiku la Qiyâma) adzandidzutsa;”"
  26,82,““Ndi Yemwe ndikuyembekezera kuti adzandikhululukira zolakwa zanga tsiku la malipiro.”
  26,83,"““E Mbuye wanga! Ndipatseni nzeru zoweruzira (zinthu), ndikundilumikiza ndi anthu abwino;”"
  26,84,““Ndipatseni kutchulidwa kwabwino kwa anthu ena odza pambuyo;”
  26,85,““Ndichiteni kukhala mmodzi mwa olandira Munda wamtendere;”
  26,86,““Ndipo khululukirani bambo wanga; ndithu iye adali mmodzi wa osokera;”
  26,87,““Ndipo musadzandiyalutse pa tsiku loukitsidwa anthu (ku imfa);”
  26,88,““Tsiku lomwe chuma ndi ana sizidzathandiza (aliyense).”
  26,89,““Kupatula yemwe adzadza kwa Allah ndi mtima woyera (iye ndiamene adzathandizidwa patsikulo).”
  26,90,“Ndipo Munda wamtendere udzayandikitsidwa kwa oopa (Allah)
  26,91,“Ndipo Jahannam idzaonetsedwa kwa opotoka
  26,92,"“Ndipo kudzanenedwa kwa iwo: “Ali kuti amene mudali kuwapembedza aja"
  26,93,“M’malo mwa Allah? Kodi angathe kukuthandizani kapena kudzithandiza okha?”
  26,94,“Ndipo iwo ndi opotoka ena adzaponyedwa ndi nkhope zawo m’menemo (mu Jahannam)
  26,95,“Ndi magulu onse ankhondo a Iblis (omwe adali kukometsa kwa anthu zoipa ndi machimo)
  26,96,"“Adzanena (movomereza kulakwa kwawo) uku naonso ali m’menemo, akukangana (ndi anzawo omwe adawasokeretsa)"
  26,97,"““Ndikulumbira Allah, ndithu tidali m’kusokera kowonekera"
  26,98,“Pamene timakufananitsani ndi Mbuye wa zolengedwa
  26,99,"“Ndipo sadatisokeretse, koma oipa okha basi"
  26,100,“Choncho ife tilibe aomboli (otiombola)
  26,101,“Ngakhalenso bwenzi wapamtima (woti angatipulumutse kumasautsowa)
  26,102,"“Tikadapeza mwayi wobwerera (ku moyo wa padziko), tikadakhala mwa okhulupirira.”"
  26,103,"“Ndithu m’zimenezi, muli malingaliro akulu, koma ambiri a iwo sali okhulupirira"
  26,104,"“Ndipo ndithu Mbuye wako, ndiye Mwini mphamvu zoposa; Wachisoni chosatha"
  26,105,“Anthu a Nuh adatsutsa atumiki
  26,106,"“Pamene adawauza Nuh m’bale wawo kuti: “Kodi simukuopa (Allah ngakhale nditakuuzani zoopsa zimene zikukudikirani)?”"
  26,107,““Ndithu ine kwa inu ndine Mtumiki wokhulupirika;”
  26,108,““Choncho muopeni Allah ndipo ndimvereni.”
  26,109,““Ndipo sindikupemphani malipiro pa zimenezi; malipiro anga ali kwa (Allah) Mbuye wa zolengedwa.”
  26,110,““Choncho muopeni Allah ndipo ndimvereni.”
  26,111,"“(Iwo) adati: “Nchotani kuti tikukhulupirire iwe chikhalirecho anthu wamba ndi amene akukutsatira?”"
  26,112,"“(Nuh) adati: “Sindikudziwa zimene adali kuchita (zomwe zachititsa kuti Allah awaongolere kunjira yoongoka).”"
  26,113,"““Chiwerengero chawo sichili kwina koma kwa Mbuye wanga, mukadakhala mukuzindikira.”"
  26,114,““Ndipo sindine wopirikitsa okhulupirira (ku chipembedzo cha Allah kuti inu olemekezeka muchikhulupirire).”
  26,115,"““Ine sikanthu , koma ndine mchenjezi woonekera.”"
  26,116,"“(Iwo) adati: “Ngati susiya, iwe Nuh, (zonena zakozi) ndithu ukhala mmodzi mwa ogendedwa (miyala mpaka ufe).”"
  26,117,"“(Nuh) adati (kwa Allah): “Mbuye wanga! Ndithu anthu anga anditsutsa.”"
  26,118,"“Choncho weruzani pakati panga ndi pakati pa iwo (chiweruzo chabwino), ndipo ndipulumutseni pamodzi ndi amene alinane mwa okhulupirira.”"
  26,119,"“Choncho, tidampulumutsa pamodzi ndi omwe adali naye m’chombo chodzadza (ndi chilichonse chamoyo chomwe chidalipo m’dziko, chachimuna ndi chachikazi chidaikidwa m’menemo)"
  26,120,“Pambuyo pake tidawamiza otsalawo
  26,121,“Ndithu m’zimenezi muli malingaliro; koma ambiri a iwo sadali okhulupirira
  26,122,"“Ndipo ndithu Mbuye wako, Iye Ngwamphamvu zoposa; Ngwachisoni chosatha"
  26,123,“Naonso Âdi adatsutsa atumiki
  26,124,"“Pamene m’bale wawo (Mneneri) Hûd adawafunsa kuti: “Kodi simuopa (Allah)?”"
  26,125,““Ndithu ine ndine Mtumiki wokhulupirika kwa inu;”
  26,126,"““Choncho, muopeni Allah ndipo mverani ine.”"
  26,127,““Ndipo pazimenezi sindikukupemphani malipiro; ndithu malipiro anga ali kwa (Allah) Mbuye wa zolengedwa.”
  26,128,"““Kodi mukudzimangira nyumba pamalo paliponse pachitunda pokongola, moseweretsa?”"
  26,129,““Ndipo mukudzimangira (nyumba zonga) linga ngati kuti mukuona kuti mudzakhala muyaya?”
  26,130,““Ndipo mukamamenya nkhondo mumamenya modzitukumula.”
  26,131,““Choncho muopeni Allah ndipo ndimvereni.”
  26,132,““Ndipo muopeni Yemwe adakupatsani zimene mukuzidziwa.”
  26,133,““Adakupatsani ziweto ndi ana.”
  26,134,““Ndi minda ndi akasupe.”
  26,135,““Ndithu ine ndikukuoperani chilango cha tsiku lalikulu.”
  26,136,"“Iwo adati: “Kwa ife nchimodzimodzi, utichenjeze kapena iwe usakhale mmodzi mwa ochenjeza.”"
  26,137,"““Ndithu kutero (anthu ena kudzitcha atumiki a Allah), sikanthu koma ndi machitidwe a anthu akale.”"
  26,138,““Ndipo ife sitidzalangidwa (monga momwe ukunenera).”
  26,139,"“Choncho adamtsutsa, ndipo tidawaononga. Ndithu m’zimenezi muli malingaliro; koma ambiri a iwo sadali okhulupirira"
  26,140,“Ndipo ndithu Mbuye wako ndiye Wamphamvu zoposa; Wachisoni chosatha
  26,141,“A Samudu (naonso) adatsutsa atumiki
  26,142,"“Pamene m’bale wawo Swalih adawauza kuti: “Kodi simuopa (Allah)?”"
  26,143,““Ndithu ine ndimtumiki wokhulupirika kwa inu.”
  26,144,““Choncho muopeni Allah ndipo mverani ine.”
  26,145,““Ndipo sindikupemphani malipiro pa zimenezi. Palibe kumene kuli malipiro anga koma kwa Mbuye wa zolengedwa.”
  26,146,““Kodi (mukuganizira kuti) mudzasiidwa mwamtendere pa izi zili pano (popanda imfa kukudzerani?)”
  26,147,““M’minda ndi mu akasupe?”
  26,148,““Ndi (m’minda) yammera ndi mitengo yakanjedza yamikoko yakupsa yofewa?”
  26,149,““Ndipo mukugoba nyumba m’mapiri mwaluso.”
  26,150,““Choncho muopeni Allah ndipo ndimvereni.”
  26,151,““Ndipo musamvere za awo opyola malire.”
  26,152,"““Amene akuononga pa dziko, ndipo sakonza.”"
  26,153,"“Iwo adati: “Ndithu iwe ndi mmodzi wa olodzedwa.”"
  26,154,"““Iwe suli kanthu, koma munthu ngati ife; tabwera ndi chozizwitsa, ngati ndiwedi mmodzi wa onena zoona!”"
  26,155,"“Iye adati: “(Ndakubweretserani) ngamira iyi yaikazi; (koma) ili ndi gawo lake lakumwa, ndipo inu muli ndi gawo lanu lakutunga (madzi) patsiku lodziwika. (Tsiku lina lotunga rnadzi anthu).”"
  26,156,““Ndipo musaikhudze ndi choipa chilichonse kuopera kuti chingakupezeni chilango cha tsiku lalikulu.”
  26,157,“Koma iwo adaipha; ndipo adali odzinena (pamene chidadza chilango cha Allah)
  26,158,"“Choncho chilango (cha Allah) chidawaononga, ndithu pa zimenezi pali phunziro; koma ambiri a iwo sadali okhulupirira"
  26,159,"“Ndipo, ndithu Mbuye wako, Iye Ngwamphamvu zoposa; wachisoni chosatha"
  26,160,“Anthu a Luti adatsutsa atumiki
  26,161,"“Pamene m’bale wawo Luti adanena kwa iwo (kuti): “Kodi simuopa (Allah)?”"
  26,162,““Ndithu ine ndine Mtumiki wokhulupirika kwa inu.”
  26,163,““Choncho muopeni Allah ndipo ndimvereni.”
  26,164,““Ndipo sindikupemphani malipiro pa zimenezi; palibe komwe kuli malipiro anga koma kwa Mbuye wazolengedwa.”
  26,165,““Kodi mukugonana ndi amuna (anzanu) muzolengedwa (za Allah)
  26,166,““Ndikusiya amene Mbuye wanu adakulengerani kuti akhale akazi anu? Ndithu inu ndinu anthu olumpha malire.”
  26,167,"“Iwo adati: “Ngati susiya (izi), E iwe Luti! ndithu ukhala mmodzi wa opirikitsidwa.”"
  26,168,"“Iye adati: “Ndithu ine ndine m’modzi wakuzida izi zochita zanu (choncho Sindisiya kuzidzudzula).”"
  26,169,““E Mbuye wanga! Ndipulumutseni ine ndi banja langa ku (matsoka a) zimene akuchita.”
  26,170,“Ndipo tidampulumutsa iye ndi onse a pa banja lake
  26,171,“Kupatula nkhalamba yaikazi idali mwa otsalira m’mbuyo
  26,172,“Titatero tidawaononga enawo
  26,173,"“Ndipo tidawavumbwitsira mvula (yamiyala); iyipirenji, mvula ya ochenjezedwa"
  26,174,“Ndithu pazimenezi pali malingaliro. Koma ambiri a iwo sadali okhulupirira
  26,175,"“Ndipo, ndithu Mbuye wako, Ngwamphamvu kwambiri; Ngwachisoni chosatha"
  26,176,“Anthu a m’dziko lamitengo yambiri (Madiana) adatsutsa atumiki
  26,177,"“(Akumbutse) pamene (Mneneri) Shuaib adati kwa iwo: “Kodi simuopa (Allah)?”"
  26,178,““Ndithu ndine Mtumiki wokhulupirika kwa inu.”
  26,179,““Choncho muopeni Allah ndipo ndimvereni.”
  26,180,““Ndipo sindikupemphani malipiro pa zimenezi; kulibe malipiro anga koma kwa (Allah) Mbuye wa zolengedwa.”
  26,181,"““Kwaniritsani mulingo (pamalonda pamene mukupima), ndipo musakhale mwaopungula (mulingo).”"
  26,182,““Ndipo yesani ndi sikelo yolungama (yolondola).”
  26,183,"““Ndipo musawachepetsere anthu zinthu zawo, ndiponso musayende padziko uku mukuononga.”"
  26,184,““Ndipo muopeni amene adalenga inu ndiponso zolengedwa zoyamba (zimene zidanka kale).”
  26,185,"“Iwo adati: “Ndithu iwe ndi mmodzi wa olodzedwa.”"
  26,186,"““Ndipo iwe suli kanthu koma munthu ngati ife, ndipo ndithu tikukutsimikizira kuti ndiwe mmodzi wa abodza.”"
  26,187,““Choncho tigwetsere zidutswa za thambo (kuti zitiononge) ngati uli mmodzi wa onena zoona.”
  26,188,"“(Shuaib) adati: “Mbuye wanga Ngodziwa kwambiri zimene mukuchita. (Akadzaona kuti inu ngoyenera kulangidwa ndizidutswa za thambo, adzakulangani).”"
  26,189,“Koma adamutsutsa. Ndipo chidawagwera chilango chatsiku la mthunzi; ndithu chimenecho chidali chilango cha tsiku lalikulu
  26,190,“Ndithu pa zimenezi pali lingaliro; koma ambiri a iwo sadali okhulupirira
  26,191,"“Ndipo, ndithu Mbuye wako Ngwamphamvu kwambiri; Ngwachisoni chosatha"
  26,192,"“Ndipo, ndithu iyi (Qur’an) ndiyo chivumbulutso cha Mbuye wazolengedwa zonse"
  26,193,“Mzimu Wokhulupirika (Jiburil) udaivumbulutsa
  26,194,“Pa mtima wako kuti ukhale mmodzi wa achenjezi
  26,195,“M’chiyankhulo cha Chiarabu chomveka bwino
  26,196,“Ndipo ndithu izi (zomwe zili m’Qur’an) zilipo m’mabuku akale
  26,197,“Kodi sipadapezeke chisonyezo kwa iwo kuti akuidziwa (Qur’an) odziwa mwa ana a Israyeli (kotero kuti ena alowa m’Chisilamu)
  26,198,“Ndipo tikadaivumbulutsa kwa wina amene sali Muarabu
  26,199,"“Kotero kuti nkuwawerengera momveka bwino, sakadaikhulupirira"
  26,200,“Momwemo ndimo tidalowetsera kuitsutsa (Qur’an) m’mitima ya oipa
  26,201,“Sangaikhulupirire kufikira ataona chilango chowawa
  26,202,“Choncho chidzawadzera mwadzidzidzi pomwe iwo sakuzindikira
  26,203,"“Tero adzayamba kunena: “Kodi ife tipatsidwa nthawi (yoti tilape)?”"
  26,204,“Kodi akuchifulumizitsa chilango Chathu
  26,205,"“Kodi ukuona bwanji, ngati titawasangalatsa zaka (zankhaninkhani)"
  26,206,“Kenako nkuwadzera (chilango) chomwe adalonjezedwa
  26,207,“Sizidawathandize zomwe adali kusangalatsidwa nazozo
  26,208,“Ndipo sitidauononge mudzi uliwonse koma udali ndi achenjezi
  26,209,“(Kuti akhale) chikumbutso. Ndipo sitidali osalungama (powaononga popanda kuwachenjeza)
  26,210,“Ndipo asatana sadaivumbulutse (iyi Qur’an monga osakhulupirira akunenera monyoza)
  26,211,“Ndipo sikoyenera kwa iwo (kuivumbulutsa Qur’an) ndiponso sangathe
  26,212,“Ndithu iwo ngotsekerezedwa kumvetsera (zimene angelo amalankhula kumwamba)
  26,213,"“Choncho usapembedze mulungu wina pamodzi ndi Allah, kuti ungakhale mwa olangidwa"
  26,214,“Ndipo achenjeze abale ako a pafupi
  26,215,“Ndipo fungatira ndi phiko lako amene akutsata mwa okhulupirira. (Ukhale wachifundo kwa iwo)
  26,216,"“Ngati atakunyoza, nena: “Ine ndili kutali ndi zimene mukuchitazo.”"
  26,217,“Ndipo tsamira kwa (Mbuye wako) Mwini mphamvu zoposa; Wachisoni chosatha
  26,218,“Yemwe akukuona pamene ukuimilira (pamapemphero)
  26,219,“Ndikutembenukatembenuka kwako (pogwetsa mphumi yako pansi ndi kudzuka ndi kuimilira) pamodzi ndi ogwetsa mphumi pansi (polambira Allah)
  26,220,“Ndithu Iye Ngwakumva; Ngodziwa chilichonse
  26,221,“Kodi ndikuuzeni amene asatana amawatsikira
  26,222,“Amamtsikira yense wabodza lamkunkhuniza; wamachimo
  26,223,“Amawaponyera (asatana anzawo a mu anthu) zimene azimva. Koma ambiri a iwo ngabodza
  26,224,“Ndipo alakatuli (olakatula zopanda phindu) amatsatidwa ndi (anthu) opotoka
  26,225,“Kodi suona kuti iwo akungoyumbayumba m’chigwa chilichonse (chamawu)
  26,226,“Ndithunso iwo akunena zomwe sachita
  26,227,"“Kupatula amene akhulupirira ndikumachita zabwino, ndikumamtchula Allah mowirikiza, ndikuzipulumutsa okha pambuyo pochitiridwa zoipa. Ndipo posachedwa amene adzichitira okha zoipa adziwa kotembenukira komwe adzatembenukire"